  "title": "-NEW- 24 Months Junior HR Executive",
  "description": "<p>Job Responsibilities:</p><p>·       SupportHR operations across multiple functions to ensure alignment with organisationalobjectives</p><p>·       Identifyskills and competency gaps, and support talent development and workforceplanning initiatives</p><p>·       Reviewend-to-end talent acquisition processes and recommend continuous improvementsto enhance hiring effectiveness</p><p>·       Supportfull-cycle recruitment activities, including sourcing, screening, coordinationof interviews, and onboarding</p><p>·       ImplementHR policies, procedures, and strategies, ensuring compliance with companystandards and regulatory requirements</p><p>·       Identifyareas for improvement and support the implementation of performance managementsystems and HR initiatives</p><p>·       Ensuresmooth execution of employee lifecycle processes, including onboarding,transfers, confirmations, and exits</p><p>·       Maintainaccurate and timely updates of employee records in the HRIS database</p><p>·       Supportad hoc HR projects and tasks as assigned<br /><br /></p><p>Job Requirements</p><p>·       Minimum Degreein a related discipline</p><p>·       Minimum 1 years of relevant experience </p><p>·       Able tostart immediately or within short notice</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Interested candidates, kindlyemail your detailed resumes in MS word format to <a href=\"mailto:josephkoh@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">joseph.koh@ambition.com.sg</a></p><p>Attention to Joseph Koh Wei Jie(R1873431)</p><p>Shortlisted candidates will benotified</p><p><a href=\"http://www.ambition.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.ambition.com.sg</a></p><p>EA Registration Number: R1873431</p><p>Data provided is for recruitmentpurposes only</p><p>Business Registration Number:200611680D. License Number: 10C5117</p>",
